 numbers of stars and distinct\nchemical abundance patterns, than in current models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Jan 2008 02:14:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 25 Apr 2008 18:12:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
